NK133(po)005:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma shin tu rgyas pa'i dkar chag
NK133(po)005:2: dwangs gsal 'phrul gyi me long zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK133(po)005:4: mchod par brjod cing brtsam par dam bca' ba /
NK133(po)005:5: gang gis dang po dam pa'i chos 'tshol skabs //
NK133(po)005:6: legs bshad tshigs bcad gcig gi ched du yang //
NK133(po)005:7: longs spyod yum sras yan lag srog dbang bcas //
NK133(po)005:8: lan mang btang ba'i rnam thar de la 'dud //
NK133(po)005:9: brgyud gsuma bla ma'i byin rlabs kun 'dus sku //
NK133(po)005:10: sde gsuma klong dgu'i zab chos stsol mdzad gsunga //
NK133(po)005:11: dus gsuma srid zhi sa ler mkhyen pa'i thugsa //
NK133(po)005:12: gsang gsuma gcig bsdus pad+ma k+aa rar basngagasa //
NK133(po)005:13: mkhyena pa'i nyi ma zhi dbyings snyoms mi zhugs //
NK133(po)005:14: brtsa ba'i dung zla snying rjes 'gro la gzigs //
NK133(po)005:15: nus mthu'i phrin las skar tshogs bzhin bkra ba'i //
NK133(po)005:16: rgyal sras na rim byon dang 'byon par bstod //
NK133(po)005:17: kun bzang rdor sems dga' rab rdo rje chos //
NK133(po)005:18: rigs can dra ma lnga dang klu thogs zung //
NK133(po)005:19: 'od srung che sogs 'phags bod bka'i sdud por //
NK133(po)005:20: gsol ba 'debs so mkhyen brtse nus mthu stsol //
NK133(po)005:21: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bee ro ska cog zhang //
NK133(po)005:22: nang rgyud sde gsum 'dzin mkhas gnyag gnubs zur //
NK133(po)005:23: smra ba'i dbang phyug rong klong mi pham sogs //
NK133(po)005:24: snga 'gyur rig 'dzin brgyud par bcas pa rgyal //
NK133(po)005:25: mkhas slob chos gsum ring lugs bka' ma'i gzhung //
NK133(po)005:26: bka' yi sdud po smin gling sku mched dang //
NK133(po)005:27: gzhan phan mtha' yas mdo sngags bstan 'dzin dpal //
NK133(po)005:28: ye shes rdo rje mun sel bcas par 'dud //
NK133(po)005:29: rgyal bstan snying po snga 'gyur theg rim dgu'i //
NK133(po)005:30: chos kyi bcud phyung bka' ma yid bzhin dbang //
NK133(po)005:31: rgyud gzhung phrin chog rgyab chos mtha' dag kun //
NK133(po)005:32: phyogs gcig bsgrigs pa'i bzhugs byang 'dir gsal bya //
NK133(po)005:33: zhes tshigs su bcad pa nyung ngus sngun bsus te gang 'bri bar bya ba la rgyan las /
NK133(po)005:34: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab /
NK133(po)005:35: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yis //
NK133(po)005:36: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK133(po)005:37: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK133(po)005:38: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK133(po)005:39: zhes gsungs na bdag la bye brag shan 'byed kyi
NK133(po)005:40: tshig la mkhas pa'i yon tan tsam yang mi ldan
NK133(po)005:41: pas bstan bcos rtsom pa'i rgyu mi tshang mod /
NK133(po)005:42: bla ma dang lhag lha la gnang ba zhus te
NK133(po)005:43: lo rgyus zin tho tsam 'god pa dang dkar chag
NK133(po)005:44: kha gsal zhig 'bri bar dgos pa phran bu 'dug
NK133(po)005:45: snyam nas gzhan gyis ma bskul yang rang gis brtsam
NK133(po)005:46: par dam bca' khul byas pa yin no //
NK133(po)005:47: spyir rgyal ba'i bka' bsdu tshul /
NK133(po)005:48: de la phan bde ma lus pa'i 'byung gnas kun
NK133(po)005:49: mkhyen rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che 'di ni
NK133(po)005:50: / gdul bya thun mong gi ngo skal du /
NK133(po)005:51: mi lo nyis stong lnga brgya tsam gyi sngon la
NK133(po)005:52: bdag cag gi ston pa sh+aakya seng ge rgya gar
NK133(po)005:53: 'phags pa'i yul rdo rje gdan du mngon par rdzogs
NK133(po)005:54: par sangs rgyas / yul w+aa ra na s+air bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos 'khor bskor /
NK133(po)005:55: bya rgod phung po'i rir bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos 'khor bskor /
NK133(po)005:56: yangs pa can sogs yul ma nges par bka' tha
NK133(po)005:57: ma nges pa legs par 'byed pa'i chos 'khor bskor
NK133(po)005:58: te nyan thos nye 'khor bcu sh+aa ri'i bu dang
NK133(po)005:67: nye bar 'khor sogs kyis theg dman bka'i bsdu bar mdzad /
NK133(po)005:68: de yang bka' bsdu dang po ni /
NK133(po)005:69: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i phyi lor gnas
NK133(po)005:70: rgyal po'i khab tu rgyal po ma skyes dgras sbyin
NK133(po)005:71: bdag mdzad nas 'od srung la sogs pa'i dgra bcom
NK133(po)005:72: pa lnga brgya 'dus te nye ba 'khor gyis 'dul
NK133(po)005:73: ba dang / kun dga' bos mdo sde /
NK133(po)005:74: 'od srung chen pos mngon pa bcas sde snod rnams bsdus /
NK133(po)005:76: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgya dang
NK133(po)005:77: bcu song mtshams su gnas yangs pa can kusma pu
NK133(po)005:78: ri'i gtsug lag khang du rgyal po d+harma a sho
NK133(po)005:79: ka ste chos rgyal mya ngan med kyis yon sbyar
NK133(po)005:80: te dgra bcom grags pa dang thams cad 'dod la
NK133(po)005:81: sogs pa'i dgra bcom pa bdun brgyas rung min gzhi
NK133(po)005:82: bcu bsal ba sogs kyis chos min sun phyung zhing
NK133(po)005:83: sde snod gsum tshar gcig legs par bton te bsdu
NK133(po)005:84: bar mdzad / bka' bsdu gsum pa ni /
NK133(po)005:85: ston pa gshegs nas lo sum brgya tsam na gnas
NK133(po)005:86: kha che me tog brtsegs pa'i kun dga' ra bar
NK133(po)005:87: rgyal po kanish+ka sa sbyin bdag byas te rtsibs log
NK133(po)005:88: dang ba su mi tra sogs dgra bcom pa lnga
NK133(po)005:89: brgya dang / sde snod 'dzin pa btsun pa chen
NK133(po)005:90: po lnga stong 'dus nas nyan thos kyi sde gyes
NK133(po)005:91: pa bco brgyad po thams cad bkar sgrub cing 'dul
NK133(po)005:93: mdo sde dang mngon pa sngar yi ger ma 'khod
NK133(po)005:94: pa rnams kyang yi ger bkod nas bsdu bar mdzad
NK133(po)005:95: pa'o // theg dman las che ba bdun gyis 'phags
NK133(po)005:96: pa'i theg pa chen po'i bka'i bsdu bar mdzad tshul
NK133(po)005:97: pa'o // ni / ston pa sh+aakya thub pa yul
NK133(po)005:98: r+ts+wa mchog grong du dgongs pa mya ngan las 'das
NK133(po)005:99: pa'i tshul bstan te zhag bdun phrag gcig song rjes
NK133(po)005:100: rgyal po'i khab kyi lho phyogs bi ma sam+b+ha ba'i
NK133(po)005:101: ri la rgyal sras 'bum phrag bcu 'dus te 'jam
NK133(po)005:104: phyag na rdo rjes mdo sde bcas bsdus pa dang /
NK133(po)005:105: rjes su dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub dang rgyal
NK133(po)005:106: sras chen po thogs med sogs kyis kyang theg chen
NK133(po)005:108: gsang sngags thun mong gi rgyud sde bcas pa bka'i bsdu bar mdzad cing dar spel btang /
NK133(po)005:109: de bzhin du rigs gsum sems dpas lha klu gnod
NK133(po)005:110: sbyin gyi gnas so sor thun min nang rgyud sde
NK133(po)005:111: gsum gyi bka' bsdu mdzad la /
NK133(po)005:112: mi yul du rgyal po dzahdang dga' rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)005:113: bi ma la mi tra sogs la rigs gsum sems
NK133(po)005:114: dpas byin gyis rlabs pas thun min nang rgyud sde
NK133(po)005:115: gsum gyi bka' bsdus shing spel /
NK133(po)005:116: grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po brgyad kyis sgrub pa chen po sde brgyad spel /
NK133(po)005:117: gzhan yang grub chen brgyad cu rtsa bzhi /
NK133(po)005:119: mkhas pa sgo drug la sogs grub pa'i dbang phyug
NK133(po)005:120: rnams kyis smin grol chos kyi rgyun du ma spel
NK133(po)005:121: te rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul du mdo sngags gnyis
NK133(po)005:122: ka'i bstan pa shin tu dar bar mdzad pa'o //
NK133(po)005:123: bye brag nang rgyud sde gsum gyi byung rim /
NK133(po)005:124: bye brag thun min nang rgyud sde gsum gyi byung rim cung zad gsal bar zhu ba ni /
NK133(po)005:125: sngon gyi yig cha khungs thub dag tu 'khod pa ltar te /
NK133(po)005:126: de yang skal ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis rdo
NK133(po)005:127: rje theg pa'i lta sgom spyod pa'i rnam bzhag thun
NK133(po)005:128: mong ma yin pa dag thos pa tsam gyis kyang
NK133(po)005:129: mos pa chen po thob par 'gyur bas the tshom
NK133(po)005:130: mi za na'ang / skal dman rnams kyis ni /
NK133(po)005:131: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i skus dngos su ma gsungs pa dang /
NK133(po)005:132: 'phags pa'i yul kho na nas ma 'gyur ba tsam
NK133(po)005:133: la dpag nas yid mi ches pa 'byung srid pa'i
NK133(po)005:134: phyir na ji ltar byung ba'i lo rgyus brjod par
NK133(po)005:135: bya ste / rgyud nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NK133(po)005:136: lo rgyus don gyis ma bshad na //
NK133(po)005:137: gsang chen nges pa'i bka' 'di la //
NK133(po)005:138: yid mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:140: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK133(po)005:141: rgyal ba rnams ni 'jig rten byon pa'i tshe //
NK133(po)005:142: de yis gsungs pa'i lung chen rnams la ni //
NK133(po)005:143: phyi rol rgol ba ngan pa 'byung srid kyis //
NK133(po)005:144: dang por srid pa chos kyi lo rgyus smos //
NK133(po)005:145: zhes gsungs pas nang rgyud yo ga gsum gtso bor
NK133(po)005:146: gyur pa'i rgyud sde rnams ji ltar byung ba'i tshul
NK133(po)005:147: ni / spyir snga 'gyur rnying ma'i rgyud sde bka' ma thams cad brgyud pa gsum ldan dang /
NK133(po)005:148: gter ma rnams brgyud tshul drug dang bdun dang dgu rnams su nges pa las /
NK133(po)005:149: bka' ma la rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:151: gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa ste gsum /
NK133(po)005:152: gter ma la de'i steng du mkha' 'gro gtad rgya'i brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:153: smon lam dbang bskur gyi brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:154: shog ser tshig gi brgyud pa ste drug gam /
NK133(po)005:155: drug pa dor te bka' babs lung bstan gyi brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)005:156: nyams len byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa gnyis bsnan pas bdun nam /
NK133(po)005:157: de'i steng du snyan brgyud dmar khrid kyi brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)005:158: phrin las phyag bzhes kyi brgyud pa ste dgu /
NK133(po)005:159: de dag las dang po'i dbang du byas na /
NK133(po)005:161: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK133(po)005:162: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK133(po)005:163: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK133(po)005:164: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyal ba rigs drug pa nas
NK133(po)005:165: da lta'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bar du
NK133(po)005:166: brgyud pa gsum gyi tshul du brgyud pa'i zam ma
NK133(po)005:167: chad cing / byin rlabs kyi dgongs bcud ma nyams pa zhig yin /
NK133(po)005:168: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:169: de la dang po rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)005:170: gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa'i ston pa kun tu
NK133(po)005:171: bzang po nyid kyi thugs rje'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK133(po)005:173: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing khams dang /
NK133(po)005:177: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor sku lnga lhun grub
NK133(po)005:178: kyi rig 'dzin dang rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs bsam
NK133(po)005:179: gyis mi khyab pa rnams la chos thams cad tshig
NK133(po)005:180: dang brda'i sgo nas ma gsungs kyang /
NK133(po)005:181: thugs rje chen po rang rig pa ye shes kyi
NK133(po)005:182: rang gdangs 'bad med lhun grub tu gsal ba nyid
NK133(po)005:183: las / ston pas mi gsung bar gsungs pa na /
NK133(po)005:184: 'khor rnams la don gyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma
NK133(po)005:185: log pa mngon du gyur te spangs rtogs kyi yon
NK133(po)005:186: tan dbyer med par gyur pa yin /
NK133(po)005:187: de ltar ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su med par
NK133(po)005:188: bzhugs pa de'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du gdul
NK133(po)005:189: bya'i khams su cho 'phrul chen po rnam pa gsum
NK133(po)005:191: de yang sku'i sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK133(po)005:194: sna tshogs sprul pa gsum gyi bkod pas gdul bya'i skal pa dang 'tshams par don mdzad cing /
NK133(po)005:195: gsung gi sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul yang /
NK133(po)005:196: ston pa nyid kyi gsang gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK133(po)005:197: dbyings las skye med mtshon pa'i yi ge a nyid
NK133(po)005:198: rang snang ba'i rnam par 'phrul pa +aa li k+aa
NK133(po)005:199: li'i tshogs rnams las mtshon bya dang mtshon byed tha
NK133(po)005:200: mi dad bzhin don gyi dgongs pa mtshon byed kyi
NK133(po)005:201: yi ge'i tshogs su snang nas gdul bya'i don lhun
NK133(po)005:203: de yang sgrar snang rung tsam ston pa rigs drug
NK133(po)005:204: pa'i dgongs pa'i klong na rang gsal rgyal ba rigs
NK133(po)005:205: lnga la sogs pa'i thugs su chud par mdzad pa
NK133(po)005:206: nyid / gsang bdag la sogs pa'i gzhan snang gi
NK133(po)005:207: ston pas sgrar grags pa'i sgo nas snang bar mdzad
NK133(po)005:208: nyid / pa de / blo gros thabs ldan la
NK133(po)005:209: sogs pas brdar gyur pa'i yi ge'i tshogs su byas
NK133(po)005:211: da lta yang yi ge'i phyi mo brdar gyur pa'i tshul du yod pa sogs las /
NK133(po)005:212: 'chad pa po'i blo la brjod bya'i don mtshon pa'i
NK133(po)005:213: sgra spyi snang nas sgrar grags pa'i tshul gyis bshad
NK133(po)005:214: pas / nyan pa po'i blo la'ang de ltar snang
NK133(po)005:215: ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi cho 'phrul
NK133(po)005:216: yi ge'i 'khor lo'i mdzad pa rmad du byung ba
NK133(po)005:217: pas / yin / thugs kyi sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK133(po)005:218: yi ge mtshon par bya ba'i gnas lugs ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes de /
NK133(po)005:219: nyid kyi thugs la mnga' bzhin rang las mi gzhan
NK133(po)005:220: pa'i 'khor rnams kyi thugs su chud par byin gyis
NK133(po)005:221: brlabs nas / de ltar ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba
NK133(po)005:222: rnams kyi kun rtog gi rgyun chos nyid de bzhin
NK133(po)005:223: nyid du ngal gso bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK133(po)005:224: gsang chen bla na med pa'i theg pa rnams nyid
NK133(po)005:225: kyi dgongs pa'i klong nas nyid kyi thugs la mkhyen
NK133(po)005:226: par mdzad nas / de nyid dngos su go rtogs
NK133(po)005:227: kyi skal ba dang mi ldan pa rnams la lam
NK133(po)005:228: stegs kyi theg pa sna tshogs par snang bas don
NK133(po)005:229: zab mo mtshon te ngo sprod par byed pa'o //
NK133(po)005:231: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)005:232: skal pa bzang po dang ldan pa'i lha dang mi
NK133(po)005:233: la sogs pa'i gdul bya rnams la rim gyis brgyud
NK133(po)005:234: pa ste / de yang rig 'dzin mi ma yin la brgyud pa'i tshul /
NK133(po)005:235: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas lha grags ldan phyogs skyong la bshad /
NK133(po)005:236: spyan ras gzigs kyis klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad /
NK133(po)005:237: phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad de /
NK133(po)005:238: rigs gsum sems dpas lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas so sor gsungs pa rnams rim gyis dar /
NK133(po)005:239: rig 'dzin mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)005:240: bskal pa bzang po'i dus 'dir ston pa rigs drug
NK133(po)005:241: pa nyid rnam 'dren stong gi rnam par 'phrul pa
NK133(po)005:242: las / bzhi pa bdag cag gi ston pas sde snod gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing /
NK133(po)005:243: shin tu skal ba dang ldan pa'i gdul bya 'ga'
NK133(po)005:244: zhig la gsang ba sngags kyi chos kyi rnam grangs
NK133(po)005:246: khyab brdal du ma grags par sku mya ngan las
NK133(po)005:247: 'da' bar nye ba'i tshe 'khor 'dus pa'i nang nas
NK133(po)005:249: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na chos 'di par
NK133(po)005:250: gtogs pa'i nga'i slob ma ji snyed yod pa rnams
NK133(po)005:251: sdus shig dang / nges par bzhag par bya ba dag yod do zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK133(po)005:252: rdzu 'phrul can des thams cad kyis go bar /
NK133(po)005:253: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur rigs drug gang su dag /'di par nges shing phyogs pa kun nyon cig /
NK133(po)005:254: deng 'dir rgyal bas bdud rtsi gsum 'jog gis //
NK133(po)005:255: dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus shig /
NK133(po)005:256: ces bsgrags pas dam pa'i rigs can lnga ma gtogs pa thams cad 'dus par gyur te /
NK133(po)005:257: de la ston pas nga yongs su mya ngan las
NK133(po)005:258: 'da' bas su la the tshom ma chod pa yod
NK133(po)005:259: pa rnams dris shig ces bka' stsal ba dang /
NK133(po)005:260: 'khor gyi nang nas rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po ku
NK133(po)005:261: dza ra zhes bya ba de rang gi stan las
NK133(po)005:262: langs te seng ge'i lta stangs kyis ston pa'i zhal
NK133(po)005:263: du bltas nas / khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK133(po)005:267: sa dang rnam thar la spyad pas //
NK133(po)005:268: byang chub thob par 'gyur ba yi //
NK133(po)005:269: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum las //
NK133(po)005:270: gang dag rim par bkod legs par //
NK133(po)005:271: mnyam pas blang dor med spyod cing //
NK133(po)005:272: byang chub gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK133(po)005:273: thabs chen dpag gis mi lang ba //
NK133(po)005:274: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK133(po)005:275: zhes pa la sogs pa zhus pa'i lan du /
NK133(po)005:277: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK133(po)005:278: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK133(po)005:279: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK133(po)005:280: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK133(po)005:281: mi las skal ldan rigs can te //
NK133(po)005:282: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK133(po)005:283: sngon ltas bzang pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:284: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rir //
NK133(po)005:285: grogs kyi sems da pa' dman pa'i lus //
NK133(po)005:286: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs par //
NK133(po)005:287: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:289: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po gnas skabs bcu gnyis su 'byung ste /
NK133(po)005:290: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:291: 'jig rten gyi sgron ma yongs su bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:292: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:293: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:294: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:295: gdul bya skabs la babs pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:296: byin gyis brlabs las snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:297: brgyud pa thabs kyis grags pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:298: gang gis ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:299: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:300: las rgyun yongs su gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:301: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:303: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK133(po)005:305: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK133(po)005:306: zhes lung bstan pa ltar byung ba ste /
NK133(po)005:308: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde rnams ston pa gshegs nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK133(po)005:309: rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas bdun byung ste /
NK133(po)005:310: rang gi khang steng du rin po che gser gyi
NK133(po)005:311: glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas yi ger bris
NK133(po)005:312: pa'i gsang sngags rgyud sde'i pusti mang po dang /
NK133(po)005:313: phyag rdor gyi sku khru gang pa zhig babs pa rnyed de /
NK133(po)005:314: gsol ba btab pas rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u shes nas de dang /
NK133(po)005:315: phyag rdor gyi sku la brten te zla ba drug
NK133(po)005:316: tu bsgrubs pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mjal byin
NK133(po)005:317: gyis brlabs pas / glegs bam rnams kyi don ma
NK133(po)005:318: lus pa mkhyen te slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza
NK133(po)005:319: gyis brlabs pas / la gsungs / des seng+ha r+aa dza la /
NK133(po)005:320: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK133(po)005:321: des sras mo go ma la gsungs pa ste de
NK133(po)005:322: yan chad tshom bu'i 'khor dang bcas te rig 'dzin
NK133(po)005:323: gyi sa la gshegs shing rig pa khyad pa can
NK133(po)005:324: gyi brgyud pa zam ma chad pas rig 'dzin rig
NK133(po)005:325: pa'i brgyud par 'dren pa yin no //
NK133(po)005:327: lung a nu yo ga ni /
NK133(po)005:328: yang dus de'i tshe dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma
NK133(po)005:329: lngas ri ma la ya'i rtse mor phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK133(po)005:330: rgyas thams cad yid la byas te /
NK133(po)005:331: kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong //
NK133(po)005:332: ston pa gsal byed 'od nub na //
NK133(po)005:333: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK133(po)005:334: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyer gsum bton
NK133(po)005:335: pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsang ba'i
NK133(po)005:337: gsang bdag gis ri ma la ya'i rtser dam pa'i
NK133(po)005:338: rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la mdo dgongs pa 'dus
NK133(po)005:339: pa la sogs pa gsungs shing /
NK133(po)005:340: de'i byin rlabs las lung a nu yo ga'i rgyud
NK133(po)005:341: sde rnams lang ka'i yul zhes grags pa sing ga
NK133(po)005:342: la'i nags tshal du babs pa rgyal po dzahns brgyud
NK133(po)005:343: pa'ang yod la / gzhan du nub phyogs o rgyan
NK133(po)005:344: gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling du lag na
NK133(po)005:345: pa'ang yod la / rdo rjes / sprul pa'i sku
NK133(po)005:346: dga' rab rdo rje la dpal gsang ba'i rgyud dang
NK133(po)005:347: pa'ang yod la / rdo rjes / man ngag dang / phur pa dang /
NK133(po)005:348: ma mo'i rgyud la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK133(po)005:349: de dag kyang o rgyan pad+ma thod phreng la bka' babs nas rim par dar ro //
NK133(po)005:350: man ngag a ti yo ga /
NK133(po)005:351: man ngag a ti yo ga ni /
NK133(po)005:352: yang dang po lha'i yul du dar te /
NK133(po)005:353: de yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis dpal rdo rje
NK133(po)005:354: sems dpa' la bskul bas sh+r+ai badz+ra sa t+wa'i thugs
NK133(po)005:355: ka nas rin po che rang 'bar gyi 'khor lo
NK133(po)005:356: byung ste / sems dpa' rdo rje la gtad nas /
NK133(po)005:358: gnyis med ye shes gsang ba'i don //
NK133(po)005:359: byar med rtsol med ye sangs rgyas //
NK133(po)005:360: dbu ma chen po grags pa'i lam //
NK133(po)005:363: sems dpa' rdo rjes bshad par dam bcas pa /
NK133(po)005:365: tshig spyod yul ma yin pa la //
NK133(po)005:366: bdag gis sgrogs par shin tu dka' //
NK133(po)005:367: ma rtogs pa la tshig sgo nas //
NK133(po)005:368: mtshon pas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK133(po)005:369: ci rigs pa yi rnal 'byor sgrol //
NK133(po)005:370: zhes zhal gyis 'ches nas rigs lnga'i rgyal ba rnams
NK133(po)005:371: las rmad byung bstan pa'i snying po rtsol med rang
NK133(po)005:372: byung gi dgongs pa rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i chos
NK133(po)005:373: a ti yo ga'i don rnams sgro 'dogs bcad cing
NK133(po)005:374: / rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i bcud blangs
NK133(po)005:375: nas sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas rnam par rgyal
NK133(po)005:376: ba'i khang bzang gi rtser lha de ba bzang skyong
NK133(po)005:377: gi bu sems lhag can zhes bya ba la /
NK133(po)005:378: rgyal thabs spyi blugs rdzogs pa'i dbang brda'i sgo nas bskur //
NK133(po)005:379: rgyud dang man ngag mang po dus matha'i skad cig
NK133(po)005:380: la rdzogs par bstan nas rgyal tshab dam par dbang
NK133(po)005:381: bskur te / rmad byung bstan pa'i snying po 'di //
NK133(po)005:382: lha gnas gsum du grags gyur nas //
NK133(po)005:383: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK133(po)005:384: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par shog /
NK133(po)005:386: bstan pa lha gnas gsum du rgyas par gyur to //
NK133(po)005:387: de nas mi yul du byung tshul ni /
NK133(po)005:388: rgya gar nub phyogs o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling du /
NK133(po)005:389: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza dang /
NK133(po)005:390: btsun mo snang gsal 'od ldan ma gnyis kyi sras
NK133(po)005:391: mo me tog gsal zhes bya ba dge slong ma'i
NK133(po)005:392: khrims rnam par dag pa dang ldan pa zhig dge
NK133(po)005:393: slong ma lnga brgya'i 'khor dang bcas nas gnas pa'i
NK133(po)005:394: tshe / phyag na rdo rje bya'i rgyal po ngang
NK133(po)005:395: pa zhig tu sprul nas lha'i bu sems lhag can
NK133(po)005:396: yi ge h'u du bsdus nas sras mo'i thugs kar
NK133(po)005:397: tshe / bstims pa na / de sbrum ma'i rnam
NK133(po)005:398: pa med par lo dus na thugs ka nas rdo
NK133(po)005:399: rje rtse dgu 'od 'bar ba zhig byung ste zhu
NK133(po)005:400: ba las khye'u chung mtshan dpes brgyan pa /
NK133(po)005:402: g.yon rin po che'i phyag shing thogs pa /
NK133(po)005:403: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che la sogs pa
NK133(po)005:404: zhal 'don du mdzad pa zhig byung ba de la
NK133(po)005:405: thams cad dga' ba'i rab tu gyur cing phyag na
NK133(po)005:406: rdo rje bsnams pas dga' rab rdo rje zhes btags
NK133(po)005:407: / thams cad kun dgyes pas dgyes pa rdo rje /
NK133(po)005:408: bzhad pas bzhad pa rdo rjer btags la /
NK133(po)005:409: de nyid kyis rgyal srid bzung ba la phyag na
NK133(po)005:410: rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas rgyal thabs spyi
NK133(po)005:412: klong dgu bam po nyi khri la sogs pa rgyud
NK133(po)005:413: dang man ngag thams cad dus matha'i skad cig la
NK133(po)005:414: rdzogs par mdzad de bstan pa'i bdag por dbang bskur
NK133(po)005:415: zhing / dam can rnams la bstan pa'i srung mar gnyer gtad /
NK133(po)005:416: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rjes slob dpon 'jam
NK133(po)005:417: dpal bshes gnyen la rdzogs par mdzad de bstan pa'i
NK133(po)005:418: bdag por dbang bskur zhing brda bstan pa tsam gyis
NK133(po)005:420: rgyud dang man ngag yongs su rdzogs pa gtad /
NK133(po)005:421: dam can rnams la bstan pa'i srung mar gnyer gtad /
NK133(po)005:422: des sh+r+ai seng+ha la gnang nas rtogs pa mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)005:423: de nas o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa /
NK133(po)005:424: mkhas pa dz+ny+aa na s+au tra /
NK133(po)005:425: pan chen bi ma la mi tra rnams kyis zhus te /
NK133(po)005:426: de rnams kyang brda thabs bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs
NK133(po)005:427: pa klong du gyur te rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa
NK133(po)005:428: mchog la gnas par gyur pas rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud
NK133(po)005:429: pa zhes bya'o // gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:430: gsum pa gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa la /
NK133(po)005:431: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga rnams /
NK133(po)005:433: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma /
NK133(po)005:435: sangs rgyas gsang ba gsum la bshad /
NK133(po)005:436: phyi ma 'di gnyis kyis bi ma la mi tra la bshad nas rim bzhin dar zhing /
NK133(po)005:437: lung a nu yo ga rgyal po dzahns brgyud pa'i tshul 'di dang cung mi 'dra bar snang la /
NK133(po)005:438: bod du brgyud tshul yang gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye
NK133(po)005:439: shes rgya gar du byon te slob dpon gsal ba'i
NK133(po)005:440: rgyan las mdo'i dbang dang gdams ngag sogs zhus shing
NK133(po)005:441: / d+ha na rak+shi ta sogs las gtso bor gzhung
NK133(po)005:442: bshad sogs zhus te bod du byon nas gnubs yon
NK133(po)005:443: tan rgya mtsho la bshad de brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)005:444: yang sru legs pa'i sgron me sogs nas rim gyis
NK133(po)005:445: zur la brgyud pa'i tshul ni brgyud pa phal cher
NK133(po)005:446: 'dra'o // mdo sngags kyi bstan pa bod du dar tshul /
NK133(po)005:447: da ni mdo sngags kyi bstan pa bod du ji
NK133(po)005:448: ltar dar ba'i tshul rags tsam zhu bar bya ste
NK133(po)005:449: / bsil ldan gangs can ljongs su chos rgyal rim
NK133(po)005:450: byon gyi thugs bskyed bla na med pa'i smon lam
NK133(po)005:451: / gyi mthu dang / bod khams 'gro ba rnams
NK133(po)005:452: bsod nams dge ba'i las kyi 'bras bu dkar po
NK133(po)005:453: dus su smin pas rje gnya' khri btsan po zhes
NK133(po)005:454: byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa rnam sel gyi sprul
NK133(po)005:455: pa de bod spyi la khyab pa'i rgyal por phebs
NK133(po)005:456: pa nas brtsis pa'i rgyal rabs nyer brgyad pa 'phags
NK133(po)005:457: pa kun tu bzang po'i rnam 'phrul lha tho tho
NK133(po)005:458: ri snyan btsan gyi ring la dam pa chos kyi
NK133(po)005:459: / gyi mthu dang / dbu brnyes / de nas
NK133(po)005:460: rgyal rabs lnga na spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa
NK133(po)005:462: khong gi sku ring la rgya gar gyi slob dpon
NK133(po)005:463: ku s+aa ra sogs gdan drangs nas theg chen mdo
NK133(po)005:464: sde dang gsang sngags kyi rgyud mang po bsgyur bas
NK133(po)005:465: chos mdo rgyud zab mo bod du 'gyur ba'i srol
NK133(po)005:466: gtod de bstan pa'i gzhi bting /
NK133(po)005:467: de nas rgyal rabs lnga na 'phags pa 'jam dpal
NK133(po)005:468: gyi sprul pa khri srong lde'u btsan byon te bi
NK133(po)005:469: ma la mi tra sogs 'phags yul gyi pan+di ta
NK133(po)005:470: brgya rtsa spyan drangs nas sprul pa'i lo pan rnams
NK133(po)005:471: kyis mdo sngags kyi chos thams cad bsgyur /
NK133(po)005:472: mkhan po bo d+hi sa t+wa dang slob dpon pad+ma
NK133(po)005:473: 'byung gnas gnyis kyis dge 'dun gyi sde gsar du
NK133(po)005:474: btsugs / de yang mkhan pos 'dul ba dang mdo
NK133(po)005:475: sde'i srol bzung nas rab byung ngur smrig gi sde
NK133(po)005:476: btsugs / dang / slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma
NK133(po)005:477: la mi tras sngags dang rdzogs chen gyi srol bzung
NK133(po)005:478: te sum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'am gos dkar lcang
NK133(po)005:479: lo can gyi sde btsugs nas rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK133(po)005:480: rin po che dar zhing rgyas par mdzad /
NK133(po)005:481: mnga' bdag khri ral pa can gyis bstan pa'i rgyun
NK133(po)005:482: bskyangs te rim gyis mdo sngags nyi zla zung 'brel
NK133(po)005:483: bshad sgrub las gsum gyi snang ba chen pos bod
NK133(po)005:484: kyi rgyal khams kun tu khyab par brdal ba zhig
NK133(po)005:485: byung / o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa dang /
NK133(po)005:486: pan chen bi ma la mi tra gnyis kyis thugs sras rje 'bangs grogs gsum /
NK133(po)005:487: nyang ban ting 'dzin bzang po la sogs pa snod
NK133(po)005:488: dang skal ba ldan pa rnams la shan 'byed la
NK133(po)005:489: bzla rang grol mngon sum du ston pa rdzogs chen
NK133(po)005:490: a ti yo ga la sogs pa nang rgyud sde
NK133(po)005:491: gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te dar spel
NK133(po)005:492: byung / de la brgyud tshul mang yang brgyud thag
NK133(po)005:493: shin tu nye ba zhig ni kun mkhyen klong chen
NK133(po)005:494: rab 'byams pa dri med 'od zer gyis snying thig
NK133(po)005:495: bka' gter gyi bka' bsdu mdzad de rim bzhin kun
NK133(po)005:497: des 'jigs med rgyal ba'i myu gu la /
NK133(po)005:498: des dpal sprul o rgyan 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po la /
NK133(po)005:499: des lung rtogs bstan pa'i nyi ma la /
NK133(po)005:500: des kun mkhyen ngag dbang dpal bzang la /
NK133(po)005:501: des bdag cag gi bla ma bka' drin can mun
NK133(po)005:502: sel rin po che'i bar du brgyud pa yin no
NK133(po)005:504: bod du 'gyur snga phyi dang brgyud pa'i phyag srol
NK133(po)005:505: tha dad pa'i dbang gis sa dge bka' rnying sogs
NK133(po)005:506: grub mtha' tha dad pa du ma zhig byung mod
NK133(po)005:507: / gangs can bshad pa'i bka' babs bcu dang sgrub pa'i bka' babs brgyad de /
NK133(po)005:508: bshad sgrub shing rta bco brgyad po thams cad kun
NK133(po)005:509: mkhyen nyi ma'i gnyen gyi bstan pa las logs su
NK133(po)005:510: ma mchis pas chos brgyad la rgyas ris su mi
NK133(po)005:511: gcad par / dad pa dang dag snang phyogs med du 'chang zhing /
NK133(po)005:512: thugs gtsigs gcig par gnang 'os pa ni smos ma dgos mod /
NK133(po)005:513: skabs su bab pa'i brjod bya rtsal du bton nas
NK133(po)005:514: zhu bar bya ba ni khyad chos che ba drug
NK133(po)005:515: ldan snga 'gyur rnying ma ba 'di yin la /
NK133(po)005:516: de'ang sngon chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan dgung lo
NK133(po)005:517: bcu gsum par chol gsum bod kyi rgyal srid la
NK133(po)005:518: mnga' dbang bsgyur / nyi shu bar rgyal bstan dar
NK133(po)005:519: bar mdzad pa'i dgongs bzhed du lang kar gshegs pa
NK133(po)005:520: mnga' dbang bsgyur / las / de yi 'og tu byas dus la //
NK133(po)005:521: 'dren pa blo gros zhes bya ba //
NK133(po)005:522: shes bya lnga rnams ston pa po //
NK133(po)005:524: zhes bde bar gshegs pa'i lung gis zin pa za
NK133(po)005:525: hor gyi mkhan po bo d+hi sa t+wa gdan drangs
NK133(po)005:526: nas bod kyi ban de rba gsal snang /
NK133(po)005:527: pa gor bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)005:528: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs /
NK133(po)005:531: la gsum rgyal ba byang chub /
NK133(po)005:532: gtsang legs grub bcas sad mi mi bdun rab tu byung /
NK133(po)005:533: de rjes zhang blon dad pa can dang 'bangs blo
NK133(po)005:534: gsal ba sum brgya tsam rab tu byung ste dam
NK133(po)005:535: chos 'dul ba rin po che'i bstan pa'i gzhi bting
NK133(po)005:538: lo ni bcu ru gnyis chad nas //
NK133(po)005:539: 'jig rten kun las lhag pa mchog /
NK133(po)005:540: o rgyan yul du pad 'byung zhes //
NK133(po)005:542: gsang sngags ston par ngas lung bstan //
NK133(po)005:543: zhes rgyal ba'i lung gis basngagasa pa o rgyan gyi
NK133(po)005:544: slob dpon pad+ma sam b+ha wa gdan drangs pas sngon
NK133(po)005:545: mchod rten bya rung kha shor bzhengs nas smon lam
NK133(po)005:546: btab pa dus su smin te mkhan slob chos gsum
NK133(po)005:547: zhal 'dzoms / bsam yas mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag khang bzhengs /
NK133(po)005:548: bi ma la mi tra sogs rgya gar gyi pan chen brgya rtsa dang /
NK133(po)005:551: zhang zhung sogs nas kyang mkhas pa du ma gdan drangs te /
NK133(po)005:552: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa na dang /
NK133(po)005:557: zhang ye shes sde sogs kyis ston pa'i gsung rab
NK133(po)005:558: dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul
NK133(po)005:559: dang / yul gzhan na bzhugs so cog bod skad du bsgyur /
NK133(po)005:561: khra 'brug rnams su klog pa thos bsam gyi sde
NK133(po)005:562: btsugs te mdo sde snod gsum dang sngags rgyud sde
NK133(po)005:563: drug ste gsung rab lung gi bstan pa 'chad nyan
NK133(po)005:566: shel brag rnams su spong ba bsam gtan gyi sde
NK133(po)005:567: btsugs nas zab chos sgom sgrub kyis nyams su bzhes
NK133(po)005:568: pas mkhas grub gnyis ldan gyi skyes chen dam pa
NK133(po)005:569: mang pos bod kyi rgyal khams kun tu khyab pa
NK133(po)005:572: khyad par snga 'gyur yo ga rnam gsum ni /
NK133(po)005:573: dus gsum rgyal ba yongs kyi zhe phugs /
NK133(po)005:574: rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho lta bu'i dgongs pa'i mthil /
NK133(po)005:575: man ngag thams cad kyi gnad dam pa rgya gar
NK133(po)005:576: 'phags pa'i yul du'ang ma grags pa mang po pad
NK133(po)005:577: 'byung dang bi ma mi tra sogs grub pa'i dbang
NK133(po)005:580: bru sha /'gro lding sogs mi dang mi min mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod nas blangs te /
NK133(po)005:581: gangs can 'gro ba'i bsod nams kyi ngo skal du
NK133(po)005:582: bzhag pa de nyid nyams bzhes mdzad pa'i 'bras rtags
NK133(po)005:583: yang dag pa mchims phu'i rje 'bangs nyer lnga /
NK133(po)005:584: yer pa'i grub chen brgyad cu /
NK133(po)005:585: chu bo ri'i sgom chen brgya rtsa /
NK133(po)005:586: bsgrags yang rdzong gi sngags pa sum cu /
NK133(po)005:587: shel brag gi rtogs ldan nga lnga /
NK133(po)005:588: 'od skur grol ba'i mkha' 'gro ma nyi shu rtsa
NK133(po)005:589: lnga sogs rnal 'byor pho mo du ma byon la
NK133(po)005:590: de dag kyang bden gnyis byang chub kyi sems 'byangs
NK133(po)005:591: / bskyed rdzogs rim gnyis kyi drod tshad rnyed /
NK133(po)005:592: yi dam lhas zhal gzigs rjes su bzung bas las
NK133(po)005:593: rab 'byams kun la mnga' dbang 'byor te sa chu
NK133(po)005:594: ri brag gang la'ang thogs pa med pa zang thal
NK133(po)005:595: du 'gro ba / lo brgya phrag du mar bzhugs
NK133(po)005:596: pa sogs thun mong rig 'dzin rnam bzhi'i go 'a
NK133(po)005:597: du 'gro ba / phang dang / thun min 'od
NK133(po)005:598: gsal snang bzhi'i lam nas 'pho chen dwangs ma'i skur
NK133(po)005:599: bzhengs pa'am lus ma spangs par mkha' spyod du gshegs
NK133(po)005:600: pa sogs grub brnyes skyes chen du ma sngon du
NK133(po)005:601: du 'gro ba / phang dang / byung ba dang / da ltar 'byung bzhin pa /
NK133(po)005:602: ma 'ongs par yang 'byung bar 'gyur ba ni gdon mi za'o //
NK133(po)005:604: de lta bu'i zab cing rgya che ba'i chos tshul 'di la ring brgyud bka' ma /
NK133(po)005:606: zab mo dag snang gi brgyud pa gsum du grags pa las /
NK133(po)005:607: gter ma ni sngon slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang mkha' 'gro ye shes mtsho rgyal /
NK133(po)005:608: lo chen bee ro tsa na sogs kyis 'gro don
NK133(po)005:609: dus la ma bab bar spel mi rung bar dgongs
NK133(po)005:610: te / ma 'ongs pa'i skal ldan las can ched
NK133(po)005:611: du gangs brag mtsho gsum sogs su mi mngon par
NK133(po)005:612: sbas te gter srung mkha' 'gror gtad cing rgyas btab
NK133(po)005:614: phyis su dus la bab pa na gter ston sangs rgyas bla ma dang /
NK133(po)005:615: mnga' bdag nyang nyi ma 'od zer /
NK133(po)005:616: gu ru chos kyi dbang phyug /
NK133(po)005:617: rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pa sogs gter ston brgya
NK133(po)005:618: rtsa ru grags pa'i skyes chen dam pa dag gis
NK133(po)005:619: gter nas bton te yi ger phab pa'i gsang sngags
NK133(po)005:621: byin rlabs kyi tshan kha che ba brgyud pa'i sgrub
NK133(po)005:622: thag nye ba 'jam mgon kong sprul gyis phyogs sgrig
NK133(po)005:623: gnang ba'i rin chen gter mdzod lta bu dang shar
NK133(po)005:624: gter chos rgyal gling pa'i gter chos zab pa chos
NK133(po)005:625: bcu lta bu / gter ston bsod rgyal gyi bka' yongs rdzogs 'dus pa lta bu rnams so //
NK133(po)005:626: zab mo dag snang gi brgyud pa ni gang zag
NK133(po)005:627: las dang skal ba ldan pa rnams la lhag pa'i
NK133(po)005:628: lhas zhal bstan nas dngos su gsungs pa'i zab chos
NK133(po)005:629: gdams ngag thun mong ma yin pa rgyal dbang lnga
NK133(po)005:630: pa chen po'i dag snang rgya can nyer lnga lta
NK133(po)005:631: bu dang / 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse dbang po'i grub thob thugs tig lta bu rnams so //
NK133(po)005:632: bka' ma ni chos sku kun tu bzang po nas
NK133(po)005:633: da lta rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar brgyud pa zam
NK133(po)005:634: ma chad pa byin rlabs kyi tshan kha shin tu
NK133(po)005:635: che ba rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK133(po)005:637: gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa ste brgyud pa
NK133(po)005:638: sum ldan gyi zab chos mdo sgyu sems gsum zhes
NK133(po)005:639: spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa dang /
NK133(po)005:641: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad rnams ni bstan pa'i gzhi rtsa'am snying por gyur pa yin te /
NK133(po)005:642: bka' mas khog phub gter mas zur brgyan zhes yongs
NK133(po)005:643: su grags pa ltar bka' gter zung 'jug byung na
NK133(po)005:644: zab khyad shin tu che ba yin no //
NK133(po)005:645: bka' ma nang rgyud sde gsum zhes rgyud ma h+aa
NK133(po)005:646: yo ga la rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK133(po)005:647: ba sogs spyi rgyud dang bye brag sku gsung thugs
NK133(po)005:648: yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud dang /
NK133(po)005:649: lung a nu yo ga la theg pa rim pa
NK133(po)005:650: dgu dang 'brel ba'i mdo tshogs chen 'dus pa dang
NK133(po)005:651: / man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo
NK133(po)005:652: ga la skor tsho chen po gsum du dbye ba
NK133(po)005:653: las phyi skor sems sde ma bu bco brgyad /
NK133(po)005:654: nang skor klong sde rdo rje zam pa /
NK133(po)005:655: gsang skor rgyud bcu bdun nam /
NK133(po)005:656: klong gsal nyi ma 'bar ba'i rgyud dang bco brgyad /
NK133(po)005:657: sngags srung khros ma'i rgyud dang bcu dgur bsgrang du yod pa rnams ni /
NK133(po)005:658: bka' mdo sgyu sems gsum sgrub sde sgrub chen bka' brgyad spyi rgyud lnga'am sgos rgyud bcu dang /
NK133(po)005:659: rgyud sde'i tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad ces sgrub
NK133(po)005:660: sde dang rgyud sde gnyis su grags pa de dag
NK133(po)005:661: gi bka' dang po gnyags gnyags dz+nya na ku ma
NK133(po)005:662: ra la babs / bar du gnubs gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shesla babs /
NK133(po)005:663: tha ma zur zur mes dbon rnam gsum ni zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)005:664: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK133(po)005:665: rje sgro phug pa chen po sh+aakya seng gela babs /
NK133(po)005:666: de rjes kun mkhyen rong klong g.yung rong zom chos bzang /
NK133(po)005:669: dam gtsang byams kahdama pa bde gshegs /
NK133(po)005:670: gtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)005:672: snang sog gangs snang rtse gter chen gar dbang zhig po gling pa /
NK133(po)005:673: sog zlog pa blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)005:674: gangs ra lo chen gzhan phan rdo rje gsum /
NK133(po)005:675: byang bdag bkra shis stobs rgyal /
NK133(po)005:678: rmog ston rdo rje dpal bzang /
NK133(po)005:681: rdo grub chen 'jigs med phrin las 'od zer /
NK133(po)005:683: smin gling gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK133(po)005:686: dpal yul kun bzang shes rab /
NK133(po)005:688: zhe chen rab 'byams bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)005:690: rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas /
NK133(po)005:691: dpal sprul o rgyan 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po /
NK133(po)005:693: kong sprul yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)005:694: smyo shul lung rtogs bstan pa'i nyi ma /
NK133(po)005:695: 'ju mi pham 'jam dbyangs rnam rgyal rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)005:701: rdo grub bstan pa'i nyi ma /
NK133(po)005:702: mkhan po ngag dbang dpal bzang sogs bstan 'gro'i don
NK133(po)005:703: kho na thugs la brnag pa'i skyes chen dam pa
NK133(po)005:704: du ma byon nas rgyal bstan spyi dang /
NK133(po)005:705: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa rin
NK133(po)005:706: po che'i smin grol chos kyi rgyun bzang po dpe
NK133(po)005:707: rgyun bcas spel bas deng gi bar du'ang brgyud pa
NK133(po)005:708: zam ma chad par gnas pa'i bka' drin ni gzhal
NK133(po)005:710: nye char dus 'gyur gyis yul gyar skabs byes pa'i
NK133(po)005:711: mkhas grub gnyis ldan bdud 'joms rin po che 'jigs
NK133(po)005:712: bral ye shes rdo rje dang /
NK133(po)005:713: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i sprul sku chos kyi blo gros /
NK133(po)005:714: dil 'go mkhyen brtse rin po che bkra shis dpal 'byor /
NK133(po)005:715: bya bral rin po che sangs rgyas rdo rje /
NK133(po)005:716: smin gling khri chen rin po che /
NK133(po)005:717: rdo grub thub pa rin po che /
NK133(po)005:718: grub dbang pad nor rin po che /
NK133(po)005:719: zhwa di'u 'khrul zhig rin po che /
NK133(po)005:720: stag lung rtse sprul rin po che /
NK133(po)005:721: dpal yul dar thang rin po che sogs dam pa du mas rgyal bstan spyi dang /
NK133(po)005:722: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa rin
NK133(po)005:723: po che phyi gling rgya mtsho'i mtha' la'ang khyab brdal
NK133(po)005:725: bod nang du'ang gzhis lus kyi nges pa don gyi
NK133(po)005:726: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa mkhan chen mun
NK133(po)005:729: khrom dge a rig rin po che /
NK133(po)005:731: mkhan chen chos dbyings khyab brdal /
NK133(po)005:733: mkhar legs sprul sku kun bzang rang grol /
NK133(po)005:735: a skyong rtogs ldan rin po che /
NK133(po)005:736: mchog sprul sangs rgyas tshe ring rin po che /
NK133(po)005:737: sprul sku thub bzang rin po che /
NK133(po)005:738: mkhan chen ye shes 'od zer sogs dam pa du
NK133(po)005:739: mas rgyal bstan spyi la 'dzin skyong spel gsum dang
NK133(po)005:740: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa'i me
NK133(po)005:741: ro rmang nas gsos te bshad sgrub las gsum gyi
NK133(po)005:742: phrin las mi nyams gong 'phel dang nyams pa sor
NK133(po)005:743: chud gnang dang gnang mus su mchis pa lags so
NK133(po)005:744: // bka' ma'i chos gzhung gi bka' bsdu /
NK133(po)005:745: da ni bka' mdo sgyu sems gsum rtsa gzhung chog
NK133(po)005:746: khrigs dgongs 'grel rgyab chos dang bcas pa'i dpe rgyun
NK133(po)005:747: rnams phyogs gcig tu bsdus te spel ba'i byung rim
NK133(po)005:749: bod rab byung bcu gcig (spyi lo 1677tsam)pa'i mjug tu
NK133(po)005:750: smin gling gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje dang lo
NK133(po)005:751: chen d+harma sh+r+ai sku mched gnyis kyis bka' ma'i rtsa
NK133(po)005:752: gzhung la chog khrigs dang 'grel ba mdzad cing smin
NK133(po)005:754: bka' ma'i bstan bcos dpe dkon gyi mtshan tho bkod
NK133(po)005:755: cing dpe du ma bsdus pas phrin las kyi dbu
NK133(po)005:756: brnyes pa yin la bka' ma'i mchod khag bcu gsum
NK133(po)005:757: sogs kyi sgrub mchod dus de nas dar khyab byung
NK133(po)005:758: / de rjes (spyi lo 1844tsam)rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha'
NK133(po)005:759: yas kyis bka' ma'i chog phrin ka nas ta'i bar
NK133(po)005:760: pod dgu la chos tshan brgyad cu rtsa brgyad tsam
NK133(po)005:761: sdud sgrig gnang ste rdzogs chen dgon du shing par
NK133(po)005:762: la bkod cing smin grol dpe rgyun bcas spel bas
NK133(po)005:763: bka' ma'i dpe gzhung zhes pa dus de nas rgyun
NK133(po)005:765: de rjes rgya sprul pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin gyis chog phrin pod dgu'i steng /
NK133(po)005:766: gzhung phyi mo dang 'grel ba sogs pod bcu drug
NK133(po)005:767: bsnan te bka' ma ka nas ra'i bar pod nyi
NK133(po)005:768: shu rtsa lnga la chos tshan nyis brgya drug cu
NK133(po)005:769: re drug tsam yod pa dpal yul dgon du shing
NK133(po)005:770: par la bkod pa'i bka' drin las /
NK133(po)005:771: kahdapala zhe rdzogs sogs chos sde chen po rnams su
NK133(po)005:772: bka' ma'i bshad sgrub kyi phrin las ches cher 'phel
NK133(po)005:773: bas dpe rgyun dang smin grol gyi rgyun shin tu
NK133(po)005:775: de rjes skyabs rje bdud 'joms rin po ches rgya
NK133(po)005:776: gar 'phags pa'i yul du mdo sgyu sems gsum dang
NK133(po)005:777: 'brel yod phyag dpe rnams sdud sgrig gnang ba'i bka'
NK133(po)005:778: ma rtsa gzhung dang chog phrin /
NK133(po)005:779: rgyab chos dgongs 'grel bcas tsho gnyis su phyes te /
NK133(po)005:780: glegs bam ka nas si'i bar lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK133(po)005:781: la chos tshan lnga brgya drug cu re bdun tsam
NK133(po)005:782: gyi smin grol gnang zhing dpe rgyun lag bris ma
NK133(po)005:783: bskyar par gyis spel ba'i bka' drin gzhal du ma
NK133(po)005:784: mchis la / bod nang du rgyal bstan slar gso'i skabs /
NK133(po)005:785: snyigs dus bstan pa'i sgron me bdag cag gi bla
NK133(po)005:786: ma bka' drin can mkhan chen rdo rje 'chang mun
NK133(po)005:787: sel rin po che'i thugs bskyed bla na med pa'i
NK133(po)005:788: bkas bskul dbyar gyi rnga gsang las bka' ba sdu'i
NK133(po)005:789: bya ba 'di la 'jug khul byas pa yin no
NK133(po)005:790: // bka' ma'i chos sde'i legs sgrig /
NK133(po)005:791: de yang snga 'gyur bka' ma'i bka' bsdu phrin las
NK133(po)005:792: kyi bka' stsal kho bo'i spyi bor dang po mnos
NK133(po)005:794: brtsam par bya ba'i dam bca' brtan po 'chang na'ang
NK133(po)005:795: thog ma'i sems bskyed kyis ji bzhin ma lcogs pa'i
NK133(po)005:796: thog / shes rgya'i tshad dma' ba sa kyang mi
NK133(po)005:797: nus bzhin du brtsam par tha mal pa'i chags sdang
NK133(po)005:798: rmongs gsum gyi rtog ngan dang /
NK133(po)005:799: rgyu tshegs gang thad nas mi ldang bzhin du sdug
NK133(po)005:800: rus byed par khrag dang dngul nag la mig chu
NK133(po)005:801: 'dres pa'i dri mas sbags pas zag bcas kyi dge
NK133(po)005:803: ston pa mya ngan las 'da' khar kun dga' bo'i lag pa nas bzung ste /
NK133(po)005:804: nga'i chos dkon mchog gi mdzod 'dun pa dang /
NK133(po)005:806: bag yod pa gsum gyis srungs shig /
NK133(po)005:807: ces gdams pa'i zhal chems tshig gsum yid la 'chang
NK133(po)005:808: ba'i khul gyis ma dpe 'tshol sdud dang po byed
NK133(po)005:809: skabs nas sdug rus brgyab rgyu'i gra sgrig yod mdog
NK133(po)005:811: bya ba la thog ma 'jug skabs mkhan rgan 'jam
NK133(po)005:812: dbyangs rgyal mtshan dang grogs mched karma bde legs sogs
NK133(po)005:814: bka' ma'i ma dpe bsdus zin pa rnams la khong
NK133(po)005:815: rnam pa so sos skyar par brgya tshar tsam re
NK133(po)005:817: rgan po lhag bsam can bsod nams dar rgyas lags
NK133(po)005:818: dang char sga dkon mchog bstan 'dzin lags kyis mi
NK133(po)005:819: rigs don gcod lhan tshogs la 'brel lam gnang ste
NK133(po)005:820: phyag dngul 'bab pa'i re ba bton yod par phyis
NK133(po)005:821: su gang la gang 'tshams shig babs pa sogs la
NK133(po)005:822: bka' drin che zhes zhu 'os mod /
NK133(po)005:823: 'on kyang rjes sor mkhan rgan ni zhing du gshegs /
NK133(po)005:824: grogs mched ni bya ba gzhan pa la brel /
NK133(po)005:825: rgan po lhag bsam can ni grongs song ba sogs
NK133(po)005:826: 'gal rkyen dang bar chad kyi dbang du shor bas
NK133(po)005:827: snga 'gyur bka' ma 'tshol sdud legs sgrig dang rtsis
NK133(po)005:828: 'phrul nang du 'jug rgyu'i las 'gan 'khris pa kho
NK133(po)005:829: bo gcig pu'i phrag par bab /
NK133(po)005:830: nus chung khas dman bdag 'dra ba zhig la khur
NK133(po)005:831: ljid po de tsam zhig gis non tshe sems kyi
NK133(po)005:832: dam baca'i 'ju thag 'chor la nye ba zhig byung
NK133(po)005:833: / de'i dus su gdung tshig 'ga' bris pa ni /
NK133(po)005:834: byang chub sems kyi gzhi rtsar legs bzung nas //
NK133(po)005:835: byang chub spyod pa'i zab lam gcig pu zhig /
NK133(po)005:836: byang chub mchog gi 'bras bu la gzhol phyir //
NK133(po)005:837: byang chub rgya mtshos glegs bam bskrun par brtsam //
NK133(po)005:839: lhag bsam can la shes yon yod pa dkon //
NK133(po)005:840: shes ldan 'gar ni lhag bsam ye mi gda' //
NK133(po)005:841: gtong phod can rnams rgyu nor 'byor pas dbul //
NK133(po)005:842: 'byor ldan tshor ni gtong ba'i sems ma mchis //
NK133(po)005:843: zhes gzhan rkyen dang rang ngos nas kyang /
NK133(po)005:844: thos bsam skabs su klog par brtson mi nus //
NK133(po)005:845: bsam gtan zhugs dus spong bar gnas mi btub //
NK133(po)005:846: bya ba sgrub par las kyis 'gal rkyen lhags //
NK133(po)005:847: kye ma bdag la thugs rjes mi gzigs sam //
NK133(po)005:848: zhes sogs gdung ba drag pos bla ma dang lhag lha la gsol ba yang yang btab pas /
NK133(po)005:849: dus yun gang 'tshams shig song ba na skyabs gnas
NK133(po)005:850: bslu med dkon mchog gsum po'i bka' bden pa dang
NK133(po)005:851: / lhag pa'i lha mchog rje btsun 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi byin rlabs /
NK133(po)005:852: skyabs rje bla ma bka' drin can gyi thugs rjes
NK133(po)005:853: yin nam snyam pa'i bkra shis rtags mtshan bzang po
NK133(po)005:854: rmi lam mam nyams snang du shar bas bya ba
NK133(po)005:855: las kyi 'khor lo 'di slar yang skor nus tsam
NK133(po)005:856: byung ste mu mthud du rtsol bar lhur len pa
NK133(po)005:858: ma dpe 'tshol sdud dang zhal bshus ched lo ngo dgu tsam phyi la bskyod pa'i dus /
NK133(po)005:859: nor rdzas dngul dang mi shugs kyi cha rkyen shin
NK133(po)005:860: tu zhan cing 'grim 'grul mkho chas bdag dbang can
NK133(po)005:861: med pas / gzhan gyi ljid theg rlangs 'khor ram
NK133(po)005:862: 'drud 'then 'khor lo la zhugs nas song ba dang
NK133(po)005:863: med pas / / lcags rta zhon te 'gro dgos byung ba ma zad /
NK133(po)005:864: tha na rkang lam phra mo brgyud nas rkang thang
NK133(po)005:865: bod yul mtho sgang gi la lung du mar gom
NK133(po)005:866: 'gros kyis bskyod dus khres po rgyab tu khur /
NK133(po)005:868: tsha po mi rag sar rtsam phye 'gams la chu grangs mo btung /
NK133(po)005:869: shing sdong rgan gi 'og dang brag skyibs zur du
NK133(po)005:870: gnas bca' dgos mang po byung yang sdug rus byas
NK133(po)005:871: / yig cha mi tshang ba rnams bod yul la
NK133(po)005:872: lung yul dgon kun la nyul te 'tshol sdud byas
NK133(po)005:873: pas dpe dkon dpe rnying ha cang mang po rnyed
NK133(po)005:874: / pa dang / gzhan yang rgya gar rgya nag
NK133(po)005:875: bal yul a ri dbyin yul sogs phyi'i rgyal khab
NK133(po)005:876: tu 'thor ba rnams btsal bas 'ga' shas thob /
NK133(po)005:877: lag tu son zin pa rnams legs par bsgrigs te
NK133(po)005:878: smugs sangs dgon gyi bla ma chos rnam brgyud sde
NK133(po)005:879: dge sku tshe'i bris pa du ma gdan drangs nas
NK133(po)005:880: dbu can gyi yig gzugs kyis pod lnga bcu tsam
NK133(po)005:883: gsar du rnyed pa'i ma dpe rnams phal cher dpe
NK133(po)005:884: rnying yin la yig gzugs mi 'dra ba dbu can
NK133(po)005:885: dang dbu med gnyis su snang /
NK133(po)005:886: dbu med la tshugs ma'am 'khyugs ma sogs yig gzugs
NK133(po)005:887: gcig gyur min pa rnams gcig gyur yong ched bod
NK133(po)005:888: yig sam b+ho ta zhes pa'i phra ba'i yo byad
NK133(po)005:889: bed spyad nas rtsis 'phrul nang du bcug pa'i bya
NK133(po)005:890: ba la zhugs / skabs de'i dus bod nang du
NK133(po)005:891: mi sger gyis rtsis 'phrul spyad nas tshong las ma
NK133(po)005:892: yin pa'i phyag dpe spom chen po sdud sgrig gi
NK133(po)005:893: bya ba byed mkhan kun gyi sngon ma lta bu
NK133(po)005:895: dpe rnying bris ma phal cher dang par ma ma
NK133(po)005:896: phyi 'ga' la'ang skung yig mang ba dper na dakoogasum
NK133(po)005:897: sad+yasa byumb yees sh+reb sogs rim bzhin dkon mchog gsum
NK133(po)005:898: sangs rgyas byang chub ye shes shes rab sogs su
NK133(po)005:899: bkram pa dang / bskur 'deb gzhugs gsol bzung 'dzin
NK133(po)005:900: rigs 'jin sogs yig nor yin nges rnams rim bzhin
NK133(po)005:901: skur 'debs bzhugs gsol gzung 'dzin rig 'dzin sogs su
NK133(po)005:902: bkram pa dang / dag bcos byas / gzhan brda
NK133(po)005:903: rnying myi rtog mye long gnyis su myed myi dmyigs
NK133(po)005:904: sogs ma ya btags can dang /
NK133(po)005:905: gzha' tshon nam 'ja' tshon glo bur ram blo bur sogs ming gzhi barje res /
NK133(po)005:906: rtse ne'am tse ne bya brtsal lam bya btsal gtsigs
NK133(po)005:907: chen nam brtsigs chen sogs tsa ra mgo yod med
NK133(po)005:908: / thar pa' rtog pa' bde ba' sogs rjes 'jug 'a can /
NK133(po)005:909: las stsogs pa lastsogasa pa lta bu sa tsa brtsegs ma /
NK133(po)005:910: bzhugs so ha lta bu sa ha brtsegs ma sogs dang /
NK133(po)005:911: gnyis med la gnyis na lta sgom la lta b+hem
NK133(po)005:912: gtan tshigs la he du sogs brda rnying lugs sam
NK133(po)005:913: sgra zur chag pa rnams sor bzhag byas pa las
NK133(po)005:914: bcos med / bsgrib sbyang dang bsgrib sbyangs sgrib sbyang
NK133(po)005:915: sgrib sbyong lta bu'am sgrub pa dang bsgrub pa lta
NK133(po)005:916: bu bya tshig gam byed tshig gis tshig tu grub
NK133(po)005:917: pa sogs yin gcig min gnyis deng sang gi brda
NK133(po)005:918: sprod lugs kho nar bstun med /
NK133(po)005:919: ma dpe 'ga' la chad lhag mang tsam yod pa rnams phyag dpe gzhan las chad pa bsabs /
NK133(po)005:921: yig nor yin nges rnams dag bcos byas pa yin /
NK133(po)005:922: dogs gzhi can nam thag ma chod pa'i tshig don
NK133(po)005:923: rnams ma dpe sor bzhag las tshod bcos byas med
NK133(po)005:924: / ma dpe gcig las lag son ma byung ba
NK133(po)005:925: bsdur bya sdur byed med pa rnams de gar lus

NK133(po)005:3983: gzhan la bgyid du bcug pa /
NK133(po)005:3984: tha na bgyi ba la smon cing rjes su yi
NK133(po)005:3985: rangs dang bcas pa la'ang gnas skabs su 'jigs pa
NK133(po)005:3988: skye ba kun tu mtho ris kyi yon tan bdun
NK133(po)005:3989: dang ldan zhing mthar thug gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis
NK133(po)005:3990: thob ste 'gro ba'i don dpag tu med pa 'byung
NK133(po)005:3991: ba sogs dgos pa mang po mthong bas de la
NK133(po)005:3992: blo gzhol khul byas pa lags so //
NK133(po)005:3993: glegs bam bskrun pa'i phan yon /
NK133(po)005:3994: glegs bam bskrun pa'i phan yon ni /
NK133(po)005:3995: thengs 'dir par gzhi 'di las stong tshar gcig ste
NK133(po)005:3996: glegs bam 'bum lhag 'grems spel byas pa yin la
NK133(po)005:3997: / ma 'ongs par yang skal ldan su gang gis
NK133(po)005:3998: par gzhi 'di las du mar 'phel bar mdzad pa'i
NK133(po)005:3999: dge bas phan bde'i 'byung gnas rgyal bstan rin po
NK133(po)005:4001: de'i mthus lus can spyi dang bye brag bod chen
NK133(po)005:4002: po'i ljongs 'dir 'khod pa'i skye dgu mtha' dag tshe
NK133(po)005:4003: 'dir lha dang mi'i dpal la longs spyod nas /
NK133(po)005:4004: phyi ma rnam grol zhi ba mchog gi go 'phang mngon du byed pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4005: gzhan yang rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyi dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4006: mdo dbus khams kyi skyes chen du mas bskul ba don yod pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4007: rgyal ba'i sras kyi mdzad pa rlabs po che sgrub pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4008: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4009: 'byor ldan sbyin pa'i bdag po dang bdag mo rnams
NK133(po)005:4010: kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs gong nas gong du spel
NK133(po)005:4011: ba dang / sngon rabs du ma'i thugs bskyed dang
NK133(po)005:4012: smon lam dus su babs pa'i mngon rtogs gsal por
NK133(po)005:4015: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK133(po)005:4016: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK133(po)005:4018: snga 'gyur pun+da r+ai ka'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)005:4019: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK133(po)005:4020: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK133(po)005:4021: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK133(po)005:4022: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK133(po)005:4024: rin po che spungs pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)005:4025: de yi phyir na gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK133(po)005:4027: rang rigs rnams kyi dbang thob ste //
NK133(po)005:4028: rgyud 'di bcang ba tsam gyis ni //
NK133(po)005:4030: rgyud 'di su yis bklag pa'i mi //
NK133(po)005:4031: lta ba'i don kun sems la 'char //
NK133(po)005:4032: 'di nyid su yis bris pa'i mi //
NK133(po)005:4033: sangs rgyas kun kyi gsung la rol //
NK133(po)005:4036: dam pa'i chos ni 'jig pa'i tshe //
NK133(po)005:4037: ston pa'i bstan pa srung byed pa //
NK133(po)005:4038: bskal ba bye ba stong rnams su //
NK133(po)005:4039: de ni nam yang rgud mi 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:4041: yum sdud pa'i tshigs su bcad pa las /
NK133(po)005:4042: la las gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye snyed zhing rnams na //
NK133(po)005:4043: sems can ji srid 'khod kun dgra bcom nyid brtul bas //
NK133(po)005:4044: gang gis shes rab pha rol phyin 'di yig bris te //
NK133(po)005:4045: sems can mchog la glegs byin bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK133(po)005:4047: nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam rgyud las /
NK133(po)005:4048: gro ga shing shun la sogs la //
NK133(po)005:4049: gsang ba'i rgyud 'di rab bris nas //
NK133(po)005:4050: rin chen khri la legs bzhag ste //
NK133(po)005:4051: gus pas mchod cing rab bzung na //
NK133(po)005:4052: ji srid gnas par bsam pa yis //
NK133(po)005:4053: dga' ba'i bsam pas 'dzin byed par //
NK133(po)005:4054: sangs rgyas thams cad bzung ba yin //
NK133(po)005:4057: lnga brgya tha mar gyur pa na //
NK133(po)005:4058: nga ni yi ge'i gzugs su snang //
NK133(po)005:4059: nga yin snyam du gus byos la //
NK133(po)005:4060: de tshe de la mkhas par 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:4062: de bzhin du sku rten dang thugs rten la'ang phan yon ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK133(po)005:4063: 'jim pa dang ni de bzhin rdo ba dang //
NK133(po)005:4064: shing la ri mo bris pa'i sku gzugs dag /
NK133(po)005:4065: mdzes shing shin tu lta na sdug pa gyis //
NK133(po)005:4066: ring por mi thogs rgyal ba'i dbang por 'gyur //
NK133(po)005:4068: gsal rgyal gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)005:4069: da lta nga la mchod pa dang //
NK133(po)005:4070: mya ngan 'das pa'i sku gdung la //
NK133(po)005:4071: sems ni mnyam par dwangs pa yis //
NK133(po)005:4072: bsod nams la ni khyad par med //
NK133(po)005:4074: sku gsung thugs rten gzugs sku yin pa rgyud las /
NK133(po)005:4075: bde gshegs sku gsung thugs rten ni //
NK133(po)005:4076: bstan pa nub na yod min zhing //
NK133(po)005:4077: mu stegs kla klo dag la med //
NK133(po)005:4078: de phyir sku gzugs sprul pa yin //
NK133(po)005:4079: zhes sogs phan yon rgyas pa gsungs yod kyang yi ges 'jigs te bskyungs so //
NK133(po)005:4081: lo rgyus 'di de tsam gyis 'bri mtshams gzhag rtsis yin te /
NK133(po)005:4082: de'i sngon du gsal bshad nyung ngu zhig byas na /
NK133(po)005:4083: snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos gzhung gi gras su tshud pa'i 'dzud tshad kyi khungs lung dang /
NK133(po)005:4084: bka' ma'i zhal thang chen mo'i bkod sgrig gi dpyad gzhi yig cha'am khungs lung 'dren sa ni /
NK133(po)005:4085: bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum rgyud dang 'brel yod dgongs 'grel rnam bshad kyi dpe cha rnams dang /
NK133(po)005:4086: khyad par du bka' ma'i dkar chag rnams yin la /
NK133(po)005:4087: dkar chag 'adi'ang khungs de dag la gtug pa las /
NK133(po)005:4088: rang gis gang dran dran tsam bris nas bsgrigs pa'am
NK133(po)005:4089: ma dpe gzhan zhig las ji ma ji bzhin zhal
NK133(po)005:4091: dge ba bsngo zhing mjug bsdu ba /
NK133(po)005:4092: dge ba bsngo zhing mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK133(po)005:4093: de ltar dam pa'i chos rin po che bka' mdo
NK133(po)005:4094: sgyu sems gsum gzhung phrin chog dgongs 'grel dang bcas
NK133(po)005:4095: pa sdud sgrig byas pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4096: rtsis 'phrul nang blugs te 'phrul par ngo mtshar bar bkod pas /
NK133(po)005:4097: glegs bam du mar 'phel ba'i bya ba gang bgyis
NK133(po)005:4098: pa'i dge bas ris med rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin
NK133(po)005:4099: po che phyogs dus gnas skabs kun tu dar zhing
NK133(po)005:4100: rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4101: de 'dzin gyi skyes bu dam pa gang na su
NK133(po)005:4102: bzhugs pa'i thugs kyi bzhed don gegs med yid bzhin
NK133(po)005:4103: du 'grub cing / phrin las kyi 'phel kha rgya mtsho'i rlabs ltar dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK133(po)005:4104: sku tshe zhabs pad rtag brtan g.yung drung gi ngo
NK133(po)005:4105: bor 'tsho gzhes bzhugs nas zab chos smin grol gyi
NK133(po)005:4106: bdud rtsi 'dzad med gnang bas bdag la lus srog
NK133(po)005:4107: ster mkhan rtsa ba'i pha ma gtsos mkha' khyab kyi
NK133(po)005:4108: 'gro ba mtha' dag la gnas skabs nad mug mtshon
NK133(po)005:4109: 'khrug zhi zhing bde skyid kyi dpal la rol ba
NK133(po)005:4110: dang / mthar thug rnam grol gtan gyi bde ba
NK133(po)005:4111: rang rig 'od gsal chos kyi dbyings su gdod ma'i
NK133(po)005:4112: mgon po'i rang zhal mngon sum du mjal te mngon
NK133(po)005:4113: par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba'i rgyu ru gyur cig
NK133(po)005:4115: mdo sngags chos tshul tshang la ma nor ba //
NK133(po)005:4116: mkhas shing grub brnyes rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i srol //
NK133(po)005:4117: thub bstan snying po gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i //
NK133(po)005:4118: bstan pa 'phel rgyas 'dzam gling khyab gyur cig /
NK133(po)005:4120: ma lus lus can brten pa'i dbyig 'dzin khyon //
NK133(po)005:4121: dpal yona yona tan bdun gyis mngon par phyug /
NK133(po)005:4122: shes rab rab rgyas thabs ldan gseng lam nas //
NK133(po)005:4123: 'gro kun kun bzang sa la phyin par smon //
NK133(po)005:4125: rig 'dzin sde snod bye ba'i dgongs pa'i bcud //
NK133(po)005:4126: rig 'dzin brgyud pa ma nyams bka' ma'i gzhung //
NK133(po)005:4127: rig 'dzin smyu gus spar du btab spel dges //
NK133(po)005:4128: rig 'dzin tshom bus sa steng mdzes byed shog /
NK133(po)005:4129: mkhan slob chos gsum ring lugs che //
NK133(po)005:4131: 'gro rgyud mchog gsum snang ba dang //
NK133(po)005:4132: mi 'bral dus gsum dge legs shog /
NK133(po)005:4134: chosa kyi sdong po 'phrul par bzhengs pa'i dges //
NK133(po)005:4135: chosa pas rgyal khams phan bde'i ded dpon mdzod //
NK133(po)005:4136: chosa la 'brel tshad 'dir bde phyi mar skyid //
NK133(po)005:4137: chosa kyis 'dzam gling yongs la khyab gyur cig /
NK133(po)005:4138: rgyal ba'i bka' bsdu rigs gsum sems dpa' mchoga /
NK133(po)005:4139: mchoga tu zab pa nang rgyud sde gsum lugsa //
NK133(po)005:4140: lugsa bzhin rlom mod nongs pa'i cha mchis par //
NK133(po)005:4141: par gzhi sgrig por dgongs 'char lhug par stsol //
NK133(po)005:4142: gdams ngag zab mo 'phrul par bskrun spel gyis //
NK133(po)005:4143: gsang ba bsgrags sam tshig don mi 'tshams pa'am //
NK133(po)005:4144: go rim 'khrug sogs nyes pa'i cha mchis na //
NK133(po)005:4145: gnongs shing 'gyod pas lha dang srung mar 'chags //
NK133(po)005:4146: bka'a dang bstan bcos man ngag snying po'i bcud //
NK133(po)005:4147: bka'a mar 'dus so der 'brel rogs rang kun //
NK133(po)005:4148: bka'a bzhin bsgrub pa'i dge ba kun bzang sar //
NK133(po)005:4149: bka'a yi sdud po byang chub rgya mtshos smon //
NK133(po)005:4150: zhes gangs ljongs rig gzhung dpe rnying myur skyob lhan tshogs /
NK133(po)005:4151: rdzogs pa chen po'i dpe tshogs snga 'gyur bka' ma
NK133(po)005:4152: shin tu rgyas pa'i gzhung phyi mo dang rgyab chos
NK133(po)005:4153: mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa dang rtsis 'phrul
NK133(po)005:4154: gyi par gzhi legs par bzhengs skabs /
NK133(po)005:4155: mkhan chen rdo rje 'chang bla ma bka' drin can
NK133(po)005:4156: mun sel rin po che'i mdun nas zab chos rdzogs
NK133(po)005:4157: pa chen po'i sngon 'gro blo sbyong zhag brgya dang
NK133(po)005:4158: / 'bum lnga tshad ldan gyis bsags sbyong song rjes dngos gzhi khregs chod dang /
NK133(po)005:4159: thod brgal go rim bzhin yongs su rdzogs pa thob
NK133(po)005:4160: pas tshe dang sgrub pa mnyam rin yod pa'i gdams
NK133(po)005:4161: ngag zab mo zhus myong yang bsgrub tu ma btub
NK133(po)005:4162: pas shes rgyud tha mal du lus pa'i gus slob
NK133(po)005:4164: sh+aakya'i dge sbyong gi gzugs brnyan rtags tsam yang 'dzin
NK133(po)005:4165: mi nus kyang sgro 'dogs kyi ming thub bstan legs
NK133(po)005:4167: mdo smad nyag a 'dzi rong gor mo rme khog
NK133(po)005:4168: rta'i gnam char skyes dus smon pa rgyu mtshan du
NK133(po)005:4169: byas pa'i ming tshe ring rgya mtshor 'bod pa'i 'du
NK133(po)005:4171: bod rab byung bcu bdun pa'i sprel lo sprel zla
NK133(po)005:4172: tshes bcu la 'go btsugs nas bka' ma'i rtsom sgrig
NK133(po)005:4173: gi mjug bsgril bar nye ba'i skabs te me phag
NK133(po)005:4174: zla tshes dge bar grub par bgyis pa lags so
NK133(po)005:4175: //// bdag ni lhag bsam che drag dang //
NK133(po)005:4176: tshe 'di'i snyan dang rnyed phyir min //
NK133(po)005:4177: phyi mar rnam smin re min yang //
NK133(po)005:4178: la rgyas brtson pas byas thal lo //
